{"tid":1592343,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"圍棋對我嘅提醒","createTime":"2019-09-24T14:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T01:16:40.000Z","uid":263197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12b8669018e27dfcfc079726fc256e6e8f6b071a","tid":1592343,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"近排捉圍棋玩得有d唔順手，咁我走去睇返《圍棋十訣》，有好多得著，而家同大家分享下係咩黎。希望可以inspire一下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一．不得貪勝</span></span><br />\n其意是說贏一目也是贏，贏百目也是贏，所以不要因局勢大好，而讓對手有機可乘，應穩中求勝、步步為營。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二．入界宜緩</span></span><br />\n其意是說進入到別人的模樣或勢力時，一定要緩緩而行、不可躁進，以免被對手一網打盡。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三．攻彼顧我</span></span><br />\n其意是說在破壞或攻擊敵人的陣地或棋形時，也要顧慮到自己棋子的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四．棄子爭先</span></span><br />\n其意是說在行棋時，捨棄眼前才幾目的棋子，而先使去下更大的棋或圍更大的地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五．捨小就大</span></span><br />\n此句意跟上句類似，其意是說在下棋時，先下價值大的地方，不要將棋下在小處，圍棋的勝敗是以地的大小來判，所以當然要從大的先着手。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">六．逢危須棄</span></span><br />\n其意是說如計算到有無法挽救的棋時，就應當機立斷不要再浪費棋子去救。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">七．慎勿輕速</span></span><br />\n其意是說下棋應謹慎小心、不要輕率而行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">八．動須相應</span></span><br />\n其意是說在與對手交戰時，其落子要前後相互呼應，隨時要注意對手所下的棋來判斷如何應手，以免到頭來造成不可挽救的局勢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">九．彼強自保</span></span><br />\n其意是說當與對手交戰時，敵強我弱，此時做活為首要目標，不要再有想着要去殺對方的棋、破壞別人的地盤算。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十．勢孤取和</span></span><br />\n其意是說當局勢周圍不利時，或是我方少數棋子的在敵方的勢力中，行棋應要和平相處，莫要與對手挑起戰端互相撕殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9B%B4%E6%A3%8B%E5%8D%81%E8%AF%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259B%25B4%25E6%25A3%258B%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%25AF%2580&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=622b9fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9B%B4%E6%A3%8B%E5%8D%81%E8%AF%80</a>"},{"pid":"22b7b0e79f9b7e93e730589442eecc4431bf60cd","tid":1592343,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"4ef667e71aa21855a56e933c3b1e6afc71282c84","tid":1592343,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"[突發]930三罷 文宣工作立即開始!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592295</a>"},{"pid":"77cabe040b6c084ce1ff8fb1e5c5b38676ab87a3","tid":1592343,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"[下一步升級行動] 點解唔可以有第二次佔中?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592335</a>"},{"pid":"f12362159ab2bff45690b2d6bfa133a36e3dd21c","tid":1592343,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"九同十好重要"},{"pid":"b9d4033cf4bba376d6faba789461d38e66d97b74","tid":1592343,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"九同十好重要"},{"pid":"2018719f00ac4207cc2072e36f776d2ec408fa4f","tid":1592343,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep